4.3 Extracting the Edges and Nodes Tables
To prepare for further analysis, we extract the graph‚Äôs nodes and edges components into tidy tibbles. This allows us to explore, filter, and join the data more efficiently using dplyr and tidyverse tools.

nodes_tbl &lt;- as_tibble(graph_data$nodes)
edges_tbl &lt;- as_tibble(graph_data$edges)

